# CODEOWNERS — Supervisory Procedures
#
# Hub team owns the schema, tooling, CI, and all non-registry paths.
# Spoke teams own only their own registry directory.
#
# Format: <path-pattern>  <@team-or-user> ...
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Hub: schema, tooling, CI — central innovation team must review all changes
/schema/                        @org/central-innovation-team
/supervisory_procedures/        @org/central-innovation-team
/.github/                       @org/central-innovation-team
/pyproject.toml                 @org/central-innovation-team
/CONTRIBUTING.md                @org/central-innovation-team

# Registry root (README, structure) — hub only
/registry/README.md             @org/central-innovation-team

